# Community - stay in touch with diabetes
Dealing with diabetes can be daunting, whether you’re newly diagnosed, an old
hand, or even if it's someone you know who has the condition. You may be
looking for support, tips or just want to share your experiences with other
### Your real life stories of living with diabetes
People of all ages and from all walks of life share their experiences.
Exchange knowledge and experiences with others people with diabetes.
Pump dramas at the airport to being newly diagnosed with Type 2.
Chat with other supporters, comment on our videos and upload your photos.
